FBIS3-15512 "drsov044_d_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Apologizes To Balkars on Anniversary LD0703111694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0959 GMT 7 Mar 94 LD0703111694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, 7 Mar (ITAR-TASS) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin has sent a message to the Balkar people in connection with the sad anniversary of their forced resettlement. On the solemn 50th anniversary of the forced resettlement of the Balkars, the text of the message circulated today reads: "I bow my head low to the memory of those who died an untimely death in exile and express my sincere sympathy and condolences to their families and friends." As president of the Russian Federation, the message continues, "I offer my apologies for the injustice committed."
